- Politician trading activity (U.S. House + Senate filings)
- Technical indicators (RSI, MACD, momentum, volume spikes, 52-week position)
- Optional news sentiment (via GDELT API)

It supports:
- **Single Ticker Mode** â†’ deep dive on one stock
- **Watchlist Mode** â†’ bulk scoring for a list of tickers (CSV or pasted text)

